    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        My passions revolve around the dynamic world of full-stack development and artificial intelligence, but it's more than just a professional interest ‚Äì it's a genuine love for what I do. I get a real thrill out of building complete solutions, from the nuts and bolts of backend development to creating user-friendly interfaces that make technology accessible to everyone.

